snippet.title: Alex D
snippet.description: Hello everyone! Welcome to my channel. My main goal here is to entertain you. I mainly cover 911 calls and I do it with the most utter respect possible. I gather the actual information from each call and I present it in a civil manner. I do not form an opinion, I leave that to the viewer. I would also like to explore other ideas on this channel, for example: DOCUMENTARIES , OR A DOCU-SERIES. I’m still not sure about what exactly, but I’d love to one day make something of that nature. Anyway, thanks for stopping by and hope you stick around for more videos. Thank you!
